  "prompt": "What is the main purpose of marketing service agencies?",
  "response": "The main purpose of marketing service agencies is to help businesses effectively promote their products or services, build their brand, and reach their target audience. These agencies specialize in creating and executing marketing strategies that can increase brand awareness, generate leads, and ultimately drive sales. They provide a range of services such as market research, advertising, public relations, digital marketing, and more to help businesses achieve their marketing goals. By outsourcing marketing efforts to these agencies, businesses can benefit from the expertise, creativity, and resources that they offer, and focus on other aspects of their operations.",
